  <?dbhtml filename="cifs-utils.html"?>

  <title>cifs-utils-&cifs-utils-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The cifs-utils package provides utilities for managing mounts of CIFS
      network file systems.
    </para>

